{"id": 2541, "genre": 1001, "title": "在你看来，怎样才是“走上人生巅峰”？", "description": "“成为 CEO 迎娶白富美”什么的，不是我心里想到的画面。", "record_count": 3294, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180930123440iRUawhWTKMnzX3c4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-09-30T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 301312, "content": "爬上喜马拉雅山顶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1053338}, {"id": 301568, "content": "过惬意的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373857}, {"id": 301313, "content": "一人得道，鸡犬升天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454865}, {"id": 301569, "content": "赚着差不多的钱，经营差不多的家庭，剩下差不多精力才是我的人生！ (一起唱)", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320981}, {"id": 302081, "content": "月球旅游", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461189}, {"id": 301314, "content": "能够自由选择自己喜欢热爱的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456779}, {"id": 301826, "content": "能够过我想要的隐居生活\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458797}, {"id": 301315, "content": "不管什么东西，只要你需要的时候，你都有。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456777}, {"id": 301571, "content": "巅峰是一种状态   做到自己现在的最好   就是巅峰", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099752}, {"id": 301827, "content": "在自己喜欢的地方，边旅行边生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458797}, {"id": 301316, "content": "实现自我价值的同时还能带来社会贡献", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455142}, {"id": 301317, "content": "开自己想开的车，娶到心意的媳妇，衣食开始注重品味，有说走就走的金钱和时间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977430}, {"id": 301318, "content": "不为理想和想要的东西发愁", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78222}, {"id": 301574, "content": "能做自己的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379988}, {"id": 301319, "content": "除了生死，对任何事情都可以说no。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074638}, {"id": 301320, "content": "能做一切我想做的事情，能负担得我犯的所有错", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437074}, {"id": 301576, "content": "能和谈的起哲学，科学，艺术能朋友一起惬意的谈哲学，科学，艺术。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454116}, {"id": 301578, "content": "和能谈的起哲学，科学，艺术的朋友一起惬意的谈哲学，科学，艺术。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454116}, {"id": 301323, "content": "有猫，有她，财务、时间自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127272}, {"id": 301579, "content": "想睡就睡", "image": "img/option/option/20181001014216UbwABpnvr7E4oslD.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391192}, {"id": 301324, "content": "有足够的能力可以带爸妈到处去旅游", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938486}, {"id": 301580, "content": "买得起房子看得起病", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1115835}, {"id": 301836, "content": "没有顾虑地去做自己喜欢的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458877}, {"id": 301325, "content": "喜欢的人恰好也喜欢自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456790}, {"id": 301837, "content": "当下的任何时间遇上任何事情 都可以保持开心的心情吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458880}, {"id": 301326, "content": "物质财富极大丰富，精神境界极大提高", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 430964}, {"id": 301584, "content": "苹果手机年年换新", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457196}, {"id": 301840, "content": "释然了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458905}, {"id": 302864, "content": "天生我帅何需掩饰", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465991}, {"id": 301329, "content": "所做的事为社会创造了明显的价值，让世界变得更美好一些", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 472213}, {"id": 301330, "content": "有一套没房贷的房子，猫有自己活动区域，我也没那么大压力。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188327}, {"id": 301331, "content": "安居乐业，情感生活滋润", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475848}, {"id": 301843, "content": "当梦想变得纯粹", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446282}, {"id": 301332, "content": "爱有所爱，没有后顾，只有前行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349444}, {"id": 301588, "content": "长生不老", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783678}, {"id": 301844, "content": "双方父母身体健康且性格不奇葩；\n伴侣人格健全，夫妻间默契，有共同爱好；\n家庭收入在日常支出后有富余；\n工作稳定，有一定的节假日，且是自己感兴趣的；\n一对健康的儿女；\n一至两个宠物。\n我心目中的人生巅峰大概是有的人的日常，可见我混得有多惨……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458826}, {"id": 301333, "content": "万人敬仰，所有人都记住我的名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456810}, {"id": 301589, "content": "不再感到空虚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215971}, {"id": 302357, "content": "想辞职就辞职，活的更像一个人。不是🐶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462049}, {"id": 305429, "content": "从没来过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1476232}, {"id": 301334, "content": "随心所欲，为所欲为", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930384}, {"id": 302358, "content": "充足的时间和金钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440600}, {"id": 301335, "content": "有一个属于自己的房子\n可以想请假旅游就去旅游\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324065}, {"id": 301591, "content": "不担心没钱花....", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206167}, {"id": 301336, "content": "大彻大悟", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982279}, {"id": 301337, "content": "有足够的力量保护好我想保护的人，以及事物。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894885}, {"id": 301593, "content": "不会去想什么是巅峰什么是低谷的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360615}, {"id": 301338, "content": "美满的家庭，稳定的工作、可观的收入", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396323}, {"id": 301594, "content": "不会去想什么是巅峰什么是低谷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360615}, {"id": 301339, "content": "过往不悔，未来可期。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131816}]}